named Irina Petrova.

96
00:09:09.290 --> 00:09:10.925
she noticed that there was a streak

97
00:09:10.991 --> 00:09:14.161
of infrared light from the sun to Venus.

98
00:09:14.528 --> 00:09:17.364
And that is now known
as the Petrova line.

99
00:09:17.431 --> 00:09:18.432
That's it.

100
00:09:18.499 --> 00:09:19.833
That's the dots?

101
00:09:20.142 --> 00:09:21.142
They think so.

102
00:09:21.168 --> 00:09:22.803
What dots?

103
00:09:26.137 --> 00:09:28.042
These dots.

104
00:09:28.108 --> 00:09:30.411
They sent a probe up to the Petrova line.

105
00:09:30.477 --> 00:09:32.713
and this is what they found.

106
00:09:33.682 --> 00:09:35.749
Are they eating the sun?

107
00:09:37.418 --> 00:09:38.919
They seem to be

108
00:09:38.986 --> 00:09:43.557
