teeny-weeny. little bit.

109
00:09:44.058 --> 00:09:45.459
So. no big whoop.

110
00:09:45.526 --> 00:09:46.760
It's a small whoop.

111
00:09:47.356 --> 00:09:48.824
It's a small-to-medium whoop.

112
00:09:49.330 --> 00:09:52.866
Over the next 30 years. the Earth could

113
00:09:52.933 --> 00:09:55.970
cool maybe 10

114
00:09:56.705 --> 00:09:58.305
to 15 degrees.

115
00:09:58.839 --> 00:10:00.808
So it <i>is</i> a big whoop.

116
00:10:00.874 --> 00:10:03.143
I heard that all the crops will die.

117
00:10:03.210 --> 00:10:04.878
