1772
02:28:48.303 --> 02:28:49.395
It's amazing.

1773
02:28:49.420 --> 02:28:51.121
Just that you've done it at all.

1774
02:28:52.380 --> 02:28:53.816
Very cold.

1775
02:28:54.516 --> 02:28:56.484
And. before. it was boiling.

1776
02:28:56.551 --> 02:28:58.520
