1788
02:29:46.131 --> 02:29:48.748
(Yes. you can think long time.)

1789
02:30:35.948 --> 02:30:39.118
Good morning. class.

1790
02:30:39.521 --> 02:30:43.324
Okay. Everyone take their seats.

